The Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, has rejected the results of last Saturday’s Presidential and National Assembly elections being announced by the Independent National Electoral Commission, INEC The PDP National Chairman, Prince Uche Secondus who is currently addressing a press conference in Abuja, described the figures being announced by INEC as incorrect and totally unacceptable. Detail later……….. JUST IN: INEC replies PDP, says no basis for rejection of collated results PDP accuses INEC of hoarding election result sheets PDP in early lead in Imo